{"content": "I need to multiply 505\u2089 \u00d7 717\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n505\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 405 + 0 + 5 = 410\u2081\u2080\n\n717\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 567 + 9 + 7 = 583\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n410 \u00d7 583 = 239,030\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n239030 \u00f7 9 = 26558 r 8\n26558 \u00f7 9 = 2950 r 8\n2950 \u00f7 9 = 327 r 7\n327 \u00f7 9 = 36 r 3\n36 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 0\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: 403788\u2089\n\n**Verification:**\n403788\u2089 = 4\u00d759049 + 0\u00d76561 + 3\u00d7729 + 7\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 236196 + 0 + 2187 + 567 + 72 + 8 = 239030\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n403788", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 411}